channel.title: Korean Conversation Table (KCT)
channel.description:
Korean Conversation Table is an informal gathering where you can practice spoken Korean with native speakers of Korean.
KCT meet every Friday from 5 to 6 pm at the Illini Union basement (near Sushi San).
Everyone is welcome. Please join us. For more information, contact Jeeyoung Ahn Ha (j-ahn3@illinois.edu).
